{"product_id":"rules-breaker-black","title":"RULES BREAKER I - WAFFLE","description":"\u003cp\u003e240 GSM. Premium Waffle Fabric. Oversized Fit with Raglan Sleeves. Front Embroidery \u0026amp; Back Silicone Print. Gender-Neutral. Combed \u0026amp; Bio-washed.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis oversized 240 GSM waffle T-shirt from Drip Studios is built for comfort with a refined edge. Designed with raglan sleeves for enhanced mobility and a relaxed drape, it delivers a super-comfy yet decent silhouette. The front features a clean embroidered “Rules Breaker” logo, keeping it minimal and premium, while the back makes a bold statement with a high-quality silicone print reading “Rules Breaker.” Crafted from combed and bio-washed cotton waffle fabric, this tee offers breathability, texture, and lasting softness—perfect for elevated everyday wear.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMachine wash the T-shirt inside out with similar colors. Use cold water to maintain fabric quality and detailing. Tumble dry on low heat or air dry to prevent shrinkage. Store in a cool, dry place to preserve the fabric and prints.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e240 GSM waffle fabric for a textured, premium feel. Oversized fit for a relaxed and comfortable silhouette. Raglan sleeves for improved movement and fit. Front embroidered logo with back silicone print for durability and style. Unisex design suitable for multiple body types. Combed and bio-washed cotton for superior softness and long-la\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"DRIPDRIP","offers":[{"title":"S","offer_id":46881408843930,"sku":"blinddrop2","price":1899.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"M","offer_id":46881408876698,"sku":"blinddrop2","price":1899.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"L","offer_id":46881408909466,"sku":"blinddrop2","price":1899.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XS","offer_id":46881408942234,"sku":"bl